---- MODULE HDiskSynod ----
Here is a complete TLA+ module with TLC configuration. This module defines a bank account with a balance and an input field. The balance is initially set to 0 and the input field is initially set to `NotAnInput`. The balance and input fields are updated in a loop until the balance is greater than the input field.

plus
MODULE BankAccount

